data.name: descriptionLabel.Text
data.value:
BlackJack is a common card game played in casinos. I did my best to recreate this game in my beloved C# language. I used ChatGPT to help me with the UI layout and some parts of the logic.
I disabled any form of betting/saving scores. I do not want anyone playing this game to develop a habit of gambling! Gambling is not a joke and has ruined many lives. I want this mini-game to be friendly and non-competitive. It should only be played for fun. ___________________________________________________________________________
